msgctxt "Demo132_0_Text017"
msgid ""
"\"Be sure to take the time to soothe your mount...<1.ra>That's the only "
"way it will know how you truly feel.\"<2.ra>Your advice was quite "
"helpfulâ€”thank you. <3.ra>This little one and I are getting along quite "
"well now."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
#. 2: raw
msgctxt "Demo132_0_Text018"
msgid ""
"At first, I wasn't sure if I should outfit him with all of\n"
"the royal gear. <1.ra>I thought maybe he should have to earn it "
"first.<2.ra>But it works! He wears it like a true natural."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Demo132_0_Text019"
msgid ""
"I'm trying to be a bit more empathetic. <1.ra>Benefit of the doubt, you "
"know?"
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
#. 2: raw
msgctxt "Demo132_0_Text020"
msgid ""
"See that mountain? <1.ra>That's Mt. Lanayru. <2.ra>It takes its name from"
" the Goddess of Wisdom."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
#. 2: raw
#. 3: raw
msgctxt "Demo132_0_Text022"
msgid ""
"I've prayed at the Spring of Courage\n"
"and at the Spring of Power, <1.ra>yet neither awoke anything inside "
"me.<2.ra>But maybe up there...<3.ra>Perhaps the Spring of Wisdom, the "
"final of the three,\n"
"will be the one."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Demo132_0_Text023"
msgid ""
"To be honest, I have no real reason to think\n"
"that will be the case. <1.ra>But there's always the chance that the\n"
"next moment will change everything."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "Demo132_0_Text024"
msgid "Tomorrow...is my seventeenth birthday."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Demo132_0_Text025"
msgid "So then I shall go...<1.ra>and make my way up the mountain."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
#. 2: raw
msgctxt "Demo132_0_Text026"
msgid ""
"Lanayru's decree is very specific. <1.ra>It says: \"No one is allowed, "
"under the age\n"
"of seventeen...<2.ra>For only the wise are permitted a place\n"
"upon the mountain.\""
msgstr ""

